{"tid":750221,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人上書展5樓","createTime":"2018-07-20T16:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-20T17:45:24.000Z","uid":165582,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"022e96b4c3897b56c034dcf50ec0301d5ae6301a","tid":750221,"uid":165582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:43:19.000Z","msg":"原本上去諗住食啲野，見隔離有展覽咪望吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n行到入去有個電競站，放咗幾部電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有班仲要老母帶去書展嘅垃圾00後坐晒喺度食雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我一經過就好大聲咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係化班垃撚圾00後，唔撚識玩，一落地就死，阻鳩住晒，屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有個家長即刻望住我，我再爆多句<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死返落去買作業俾班垃圾啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就頭也不回咁走咗<br />\n<br />\n毛都未生齊，學咩人食雞，玩返你啲垃圾手機驚啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51016d846c4bbcad74c1f6ab8a8c6c9a15ad17d1","tid":750221,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dd89e31f1d45a23a18a73e3a3967bee18f60428e","tid":750221,"uid":43190,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"嘩好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fed90ce3b9d77a4bfb0eb1d7d9e6b6d451c3c7e","tid":750221,"uid":151324,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T16:54:59.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"e7854519ade3a4991ee8720564438c8c42783bb4","tid":750221,"uid":44606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-20T17:34:24.000Z","msg":"人地當你傻仔咋"},{"pid":"d10ab5dccbcf649121291559fec6d2dd52b2bcde","tid":750221,"uid":165582,"l